  "original_title": "Sri Lanka to issue casino regulations, update betting law",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lanka to issue casino regulations, update betting law",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "ECONOMYNEXT  \u2013  Sri Lanka will issue regulations for casinos under a 2010 law and also will amend a related legislative act on betting, a government statement said.",
        "Though a law casino regulation law was passed in 2010 requiring gaming establishments to be issued licenses the required regulations had been issued so far.",
        "The regulations will make it easier to collect taxes, Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe has informed cabinet as Finance Minister.",
        "The cabinet has approved the issue of regulations under the 2010 casino business regulation law.",
        "The cabinet has also approved amendments to a 1988 betting law, the statement said. (Colombo/July06/2022)"
      ],
